Package com.cafean.client.ui.navigator

Class NavigatorNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.swing.tree.DefaultMutableTreeNode
      • com.cafean.client.ui.navigator.NavigatorNode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.datatransfer.Transferable, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, javax.swing.tree.MutableTreeNode, javax.swing.tree.TreeNode
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BeanArrayNode, BeanNode, CategoryNode, ChildComponentNode, ComponentNode, ConnectionListNode, ConnectionNode, MiniNavigatorRootNode, ModelNode, NavigatorRootNode, PluginNode
    public abstract class NavigatorNode
extends javax.swing.tree.DefaultMutableTreeNode
implements java.awt.datatransfer.Transferable
    The NavigatorNode is a default TreeNode that is the basis for all nodes that will appear inside the navigator. All nodes in the navigator are based on information specific to a certain model. A direct reference to that model is part of the NavigatorNode.
